data.text: If residents require any assistance during this period, please contact Tampines North CC at PA_Tampinesnorthcc@pa.gov.sg   We will do our best to help.

I still have a stack of get well cards, both already handwritten and blank ones which I am happy to send one over to recovering residents as a little gesture of encouragement. Just PM or email me with your details.
Clarification: Over the last 5 mths, HRP has become more manageable, and more residents are familiar with it now.  Hence, PA has recently stopped WeCare Pack delivery. Nothing to do with MOH.
@YamKeng @TampinesNorth Let's work with it halfways - maybe if they called in to note themselves, a volunteer could do a contact-free delivery drop.
